### Happy path: owner retrieves their own purchase (200 OK)
# alice owns purchase aa000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000001 (seed: txn_seed_001, pending, Shoply)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases/aa000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### Happy path: confirmed purchase (200 OK)
# alice owns purchase aa000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000005 (seed: txn_seed_005, confirmed, Shoply)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases/aa000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000005
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 403 Forbidden: alice attempts to view bob's purchase
# bob owns purchase aa000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000003 (seed: txn_seed_003)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases/aa000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 404 Not Found: purchase does not exist
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 401 Unauthorized: no token provided
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases/aa000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
